OL,3,CMan denies murdering wife as she
OL,4,Cpushed baby in pram
OL,6,FA man has pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fmurdering his wife as she pushed their
OL,8,Fbaby in a pram.
OL,10,FKulsuma Akter, 27, was stabbed to
OL,11,Fdeath in an attack in Bradford city
OL,12,Fcentre on 6 April.
OL,14,FA court heard Ms Akter's husband
OL,15,FHabibur Masum, 25, is accused of
OL,16,Fassaulting her on 23 and 24 November
OL,17,Flast year before allegedly stalking
OL,18,Fher and finding her at a safe house
OL,19,Fwhere she had been staying in April.
