OL,3,CMan denies murdering wife as she
OL,4,Cpushed baby in pram
OL,6,FOn Thursday Masum, of Leamington
OL,7,FAvenue in Burnley, appeared at
OL,8,FBradford Crown Court where he denied
OL,9,Fmurder, two charges of assault, one
OL,10,Fcount of making threats to kill, one
OL,11,Fcharge of stalking and one of
OL,12,Fpossessing a knife.
OL,14,FThe court heard the allegations of
OL,15,Fassault and threats to kill relate to
OL,16,Ftwo days last November.
