OL,3,CMan denies murdering wife as she
OL,4,Cpushed baby in pram
OL,6,FMasum is accused of stalking Ms Akter
OL,7,Fbetween November and April, with the
OL,8,Fcharge alleging he "tracked her
OL,9,Fmovements and located her at a safe
OL,10,Fhouse, sent her messages of a menacing
OL,11,Fnature which contained threats to kill
OL,12,Fanother and photos and videos of the
OL,13,Farea and premises where she was
OL,14,Fresiding".
OL,16,FHe is also alleged to have "loitered
OL,17,Fin the area of her temporary
OL,18,Fresidence".
