OL,3,CMan denies murdering wife as she
OL,4,Cpushed baby in pram
OL,6,FThe charge alleges he caused her
OL,7,F"alarm or distress" and to "fear that
OL,8,Fviolence would be used against her".
OL,10,FJudge Jonathan Rose remanded Masum
OL,11,Finto custody until his next hearing at
OL,12,Fthe same court on 27 September.
OL,14,FA trial date of 18 November was set at
OL,15,Fan earlier hearing.
OL,17,FMs Akter was taken to hospital after
OL,18,Fbeing stabbed several times during the
OL,19,Fincident in Westgate at the junction
OL,20,Fwith Drewton Road. She later died from
OL,21,Fher injuries. The baby was unharmed.
